title: Washington Post "Inadvertently" Publishes Article Declaring Joe Biden Candidacy
text:
Washington Post "Inadvertently" Publi... Washington Post "Inadvertently" Publishes Article Declaring Joe Biden Candidacy Next Story Prev Story 11 hrs ago Read more: Hollywood Reporter 
"Vice President Biden plans to enter the contest for the 2016 presidential nomination," the article read before it was pulled. The publication's web site published a story Monday entitled "Biden to launch presidential campaign," even though the current vice president has not yet declared that he is running.   Hollywood Reporter.
